### BadgeLife Community Information

**Event Name:** BadgeLife Community

**Description:**
- Brought to you by several contributors including Compukidmike, Redactd, Klipper, V0rtex, Mike's Wife, and BP.
- Emphasis on the excitement surrounding badge creation and community engagement.
- New features and surprises are promised for the current year.

**Hours of Operation:**
- Monday: Closed
- Tuesday: 10:30 AM - 5:00 PM
- Wednesday: 10:30 AM - 5:00 PM
- Thursday: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM
- Friday: 9:00 AM - 11:00 AM

**MiniBadge Details:**
- A MiniBadge will be available at the community booth. Details on how to acquire it will be provided at the event.

**Desktop Wallpaper:**
- The community offers desktop wallpaper available for download.
  [Download Wallpaper](https://saintcon.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Badgelife-2023_5K_Wallpaper.png)

